Package: spatialTV
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Transcriptomics Analysis with Total Variation Regularization
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-11-03
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Liu", email = "liutom@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("University of Michigan", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Implements spatially-aware cell type deconvolution for spatial 
    transcriptomics data using Total Variation (TV) regularization. The package 
    uses Fast Iterative Shrinkage-Thresholding Algorithm (FISTA) for efficient 
    optimization with weighted soft-L1 TV penalty. It learns low-rank cell type 
    dictionaries and per-spot mixture proportions while enforcing spatial 
    smoothness through a Delaunay graph structure.
